      "agressor": "teachers",
      "notes": "In 1900, there was a complaint made about the treatment ofthe students by the teachers, there were allegations of physical abuse and of being locked in a room.",
      "ref": ["00344", "00345", "00346", "00347", "00348", "00348A", "00349"]
